videos.description: Monte Morris comes up with a steal and feeds an outlet to Deonte Burton for the dunk.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Deonte Burton slams down the fast break flush

videos.description: Matt Thomas knocks down his 6th 3-pointer of the night for Iowa State.
videos.headline: Matt Thomas gets the crowd fired up after knocking down his 6th 3-pointer

videos.description: Iowa State's Matt Thomas up fakes a defender then nails a corner 3-pointer for his 7th of the night.
videos.headline: Matt Thomas ties a career high with his 7th 3-pointer

videos.description: Matt Thomas feeds Solomon Young for a big two handed slam.
videos.headline: Iowa State's Solomon Young rises up for two handed flush

videos.description: Monte Morris tops his great night off with a late steal to seal the victory on senior night.
videos.headline: Monte Morris sneaks in to steal inbound pass to seal the victory for Iowa State

videos.description: On Senior Night, Matt Thomas scores 25 points to help No. 24 Iowa State top Oklahoma State 86-83.
videos.headline: Iowa State holds off Oklahoma State
